data.description: Elegant Two-Story Residence in Riverview’s Premier Community    Welcome to this breathtaking 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in the heart of Riverview. Spanning two generously proportioned levels, this home exudes both elegance and functionality. The first floor unveils a versatile flex room tailored to meet diverse needs - be it a home office, personal gym, or reading nook. The heart of the home, an open floor plan, impeccably connects the family room, dining space, and a modern kitchen. Rounding off the ground level is a strategically located half-bath.    Journey up the gracefully designed stairs to the second floor, where a large loft awaits, perfect for entertaining or as a family hub. Discover the owner’s suite, an embodiment of luxury and comfort, complemented by a spa-like en-suite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. The upper level also houses the invaluable laundry room, neighboring a pristine full bathroom that serves the additional three bedrooms. Storage won’t be an issue here, with bountiful hall and linen closets throughout.    Recent upgrades like the plush, newly installed carpet and fresh, modern paint add a touch of sophistication. The home’s sturdy storm windows promise both safety and energy conservation. The expansive backyard is a blank canvas for creating memorable outdoor moments.    Nestled in a dynamic Riverview community, residents have privileged access to top-notch amenities including a playground, a chic clubhouse, and a resort-style community pool. This residence is a blend of modern-day sophistication and everyday functionality. Secure your chance to call this gem ‘home’.
